# Guardyn PGP Key Policy

This domain supports Web Key Directory (WKD) for automatic PGP key discovery.

## Supported Email Addresses

- security@guardyn.io
- founder@guardyn.io
- backers@guardyn.io
- admin@guardyn.io

## Key Information

**Security Team Key:**
- Email: security@guardyn.io
- Fingerprint: 72E2 35E0 C28B 3042 6434 1BF6 AC2A E8F7 04CE 083A
- Key ID: 04CE083A
- Created: 2025-11-17
- Expires: 2027-11-17
- Algorithm: RSA 4096-bit

## Key Usage

This key is used for:
- Encrypted communication with Guardyn security team
- Signing security advisories
- Responsible vulnerability disclosure
- Grant applications and official correspondence

## Verification

You can verify our PGP key from multiple sources:
- https://guardyn.co/.well-known/pgp-key.txt
- https://keys.openpgp.org (search: security@guardyn.io)
- Our GitHub repository: github.com/guardyn/guardyn

## Contact

For security issues, please encrypt your message to security@guardyn.io
For general inquiries: hello@guardyn.io
